  "comment": "COLORado™ 1-Tri Tour mirrors the COLORado™ 1-Tri IP’s architecture but is built just for indoor use, which allows the incorporation of Neutrik® powerCON® connectors for a speedier and easier setup. As with the COLORado™ 1-Tri IP, specially designed optics allow the light from the LEDs to converge before leaving the fixture, ensuring better color mixing while five dimming curves and optional color blending filters further enrich the wash possibilities. COLORado™ 1-Tri Tour also includes a builtin gel frame holder.",
